{"tid":1836341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【#黃色經濟圈： #潘媽媽果園 開放日】 x 支援義士 幫襯光時","createTime":"2020-01-23T07:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T16:50:11.000Z","uid":9566,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"744605ba34a22bf9c99f5d9c04cb5d2bd690bdf0","tid":1836341,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkongsofficial/posts/187375169320020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkongsofficial%2Fposts%2F187375169320020&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=20c36f1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkongsofficial/posts/187375169320020</a><br />\n<br />\n潘媽媽喺元朗大棠村扎根耕種33年，2018年開設「潘媽媽果園」。果園不定期開放，只需$10入場費，就可以$20/磅任摘園內新鮮蔬果。<br />\n<br />\n園內仲有 #純手工制作 #香水檸檬蜜糖 #香水檸檬茶 可供選購，全部都好吸引！<br />\n<br />\n潘媽媽近日決定將門票收入全數捐贈光時（但你懂的，光時暫不接受捐款，繼續消費已經可以了），所以光時都想呼籲大家大大力懲罰呢位任性嘅媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n果園喺農曆新年後有3日開放，大家快啲mark實日期：<br />\n<br />\n1月28日 (年初四)<br />\n2月1日 (年初八)<br />\n2月2日 (年初九)<br />\n時間：下午2:00-6:00<br />\n<br />\n感謝潘媽媽，感謝一眾同路人。<br />\n<br />\n潘媽媽果園<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=1201184626746127&amp;id=779824382215489\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1201184626746127%26id%3D779824382215489&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=376c184b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=1201184626746127&amp;id=779824382215489</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n支援義士 幫襯光時<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.HKongs.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.HKongs.com&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=92238859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.HKongs.com</a>"},{"pid":"a1a812f938822d58f1bca242e7f46c13369a0133","tid":1836341,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy